OL,3,CHealth help or ad break? ITV News
OL,4,Creporter puts hydration breaks to the
OL,5,Ctest
OL,7,FITV News' Science Correspondent Martin
OL,8,FStew underwent the same heat training
OL,9,FEngland's players completed before
OL,10,Fselection.
OL,12,FA three-minute hydration break in each
OL,13,Fhalf is designed to help players cope
OL,14,Fwith extreme temperatures during the
OL,15,F2026 Fifa World Cup.
OL,17,FBut do they really make a difference,
OL,18,For are they simply a brief pause in
OL,19,Fplay and a convenient opportunity for
OL,20,Fadverts?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
