OL,3,CHealth help or ad break? ITV News
OL,4,Creporter puts hydration breaks to the
OL,5,Ctest
OL,7,FEngland's players will find out on
OL,8,FSaturday when they face Norway in
OL,9,Ftheir hottest conditions of the
OL,10,Ftournament so far.
OL,12,FWhat temperature conditions will the
OL,13,FThree Lions battle with this weekend?
OL,15,FFifa measures heat using the Wet Bulb
OL,16,FGlobe Temperature (WBGT), which takes
OL,17,Finto account air temperature, humidity
OL,18,Fand direct sunshine.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
