OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783763359
OL,3,CHealth help or ad break? ITV News
OL,4,Creporter puts hydration breaks to the
OL,5,Ctest
OL,7,FForecast conditions in Miami are
OL,8,Fexpected to produce a WBGT of around
OL,9,F30C. Combined with the humidity,
OL,10,Fconditions are expected to feel closer
OL,11,Fto 45C.
OL,13,FThe international players' union,
OL,14,FFIFPRO, recommends that matches should
OL,15,Fbe considered for delay or
OL,16,Fpostponement when the WBGT exceeds 28C.
OL,18,FWill hydration breaks help England
OL,19,Fplayers beat the heat?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
