OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783763359
OL,3,CHealth help or ad break? ITV News
OL,4,Creporter puts hydration breaks to the
OL,5,Ctest
OL,7,FTo find out, I underwent the same heat
OL,8,Ftraining England's players completed
OL,9,Fbefore selection. Inside a heat
OL,10,Fchamber at Brunel University, set to a
OL,11,FWBGT of 28C, I was asked to jog
OL,12,Fcontinuously for 45 minutes.
OL,14,FTo monitor the effects of the heat, I
OL,15,Fwas fitted with a heart rate monitor
OL,16,Fand oxygen sensor, and swallowed a
OL,17,Fpill-sized thermometer to measure my
OL,18,Fcore body temperature throughout the
OL,19,Fsession.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783763359
OL,3,CHealth help or ad break? ITV News
OL,4,Creporter puts hydration breaks to the
OL,5,Ctest
OL,7,FAs expected, the hotter my body
OL,8,Fbecame, the harder it had to work. My
OL,9,Fheart rate increased by around 20
OL,10,Fbeats per minute as my core
OL,11,Ftemperature rose from 37C to 39C.
OL,13,FThen came the hydration break.
OL,15,FLike the players, I stopped for three
OL,16,Fminutes to drink water.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
