OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783763359
OL,3,CHealth help or ad break? ITV News
OL,4,Creporter puts hydration breaks to the
OL,5,Ctest
OL,7,F"The concept is a good one" according
OL,8,Fto Dr Oliver Gibson from Brunel
OL,9,FUniversity. "But in reality the 3
OL,10,Fminutes is probably not enough to make
OL,11,Fa meaningful difference".
OL,13,FThe data from my run backed that up.
OL,15,F"We see a slight drop in the core body
OL,16,Ftemperature" Dr Gibson says as he
OL,17,Fshows me a graph readout from my
OL,18,Finternal thermometer.
OL,26,@oD@[O]qD@MOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
