OL,3,CHealth help or ad break? ITV News
OL,4,Creporter puts hydration breaks to the
OL,5,Ctest
OL,7,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,F"But nothing major, nothing that is
OL,13,Fgoing to be meaningful and we can see
OL,14,Fthe line continues to increase
OL,15,Fimmediately after the resumption of
OL,16,Fplay."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
