OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783763359
OL,3,CHealth help or ad break? ITV News
OL,4,Creporter puts hydration breaks to the
OL,5,Ctest
OL,7,FDr Gibson believes that to
OL,8,Fsignificantly reduce body temperature,
OL,9,Fplayers would need longer breaks and
OL,10,Fmore intensive cooling methods, such
OL,11,Fas ice vests.
OL,13,FSome players have already been seen
OL,14,Fusing ice packs and frozen drinks
OL,15,Fduring the tournament. England may
OL,16,Fneed to rely on similar measures if
OL,17,Fthey are to prevent the heat from
OL,18,Faffecting performance against Norway.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
